2017-01-15 LLW

Source file src/edumip_ros_joy_node.cpp is a simple ROS node to:
  1. subscribe to a joystick sensor_msgs::Joy on the topic /joy 
  2. publishes a geometry_msgs::Twist on the topic /edumip/cmd at 10Hz. 

Roslaunch file launch/edumip_ros_joy.launch
  1. Runs a standard ROS joystick node from the package "joy", which
     opens and reads from the joystick device /dev/input/js0
  2. Runs edumip_ros_joy_node